title: 207: 10 Takeaways from Week 2
itunes:title: 207: 10 Takeaways from Week 2
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks review all the action from across the NFL landscape by diving into the ten biggest takeaways from this past weekend. The guys break down the dominant performance from the Falcons, the impressive showings from Brady, Carr and much more.
